  "detailed_description": "<strong>NOTE: This game requires  <u>2 separate players who own the game</u> to play!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Journey to the top!</h2><br>Two Climbers is a two player platformer where you and a buddy work together to climb a top Mount Teawok.<br>Filled with puzzles and platforming challenges, explore the different parts of Mount Teawok on your way to the top!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590080/extras/dc61b2629dcdea68120352efb62985b9.poster.avif?t=1706988428\" width=506 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590080/extras/dc61b2629dcdea68120352efb62985b9.webm?t=1706988428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590080/extras/dc61b2629dcdea68120352efb62985b9.mp4?t=1706988428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Work Together</h2><br>Utilize unlockable skills that allow you and your teammate to combine your efforts to accomplish tasks that are impossible alone!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590080/extras/414038d7455f85dd85eb3b11c74f0ef5.poster.avif?t=1706988428\" width=506 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590080/extras/414038d7455f85dd85eb3b11c74f0ef5.webm?t=1706988428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590080/extras/414038d7455f85dd85eb3b11c74f0ef5.mp4?t=1706988428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find Secret Collectables!</h2><br>Hidden Moons can be found throughout Mount Teawok!<br>Can you find them all?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590080/extras/13538c4f002d0419fd32e6d32b3602a4.poster.avif?t=1706988428\" width=506 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590080/extras/13538c4f002d0419fd32e6d32b3602a4.webm?t=1706988428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590080/extras/13538c4f002d0419fd32e6d32b3602a4.mp4?t=1706988428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
